name: Negate
website_url: https://negate.io
privacy_policy_url: https://negate.io/privacy
privacy_contact: privacy@negate.io
country: US
description: Negate LLC is the developer of a fraud preventive tool designed to enable businesses to protect their store from ad fraud. The company offers a simple plug-and-play platform that helps businesses to avoid being targeted by bot farms designed to drain their paid advertisement budget and stop them at the source, thereby enabling businesses to protect their online store from fake clicks.
